CONCAT CSECT
*THIS SUBROUTINE IS CALLED BY A PROGRAM REQUIRING CONCATENATION
*OF DATASETS WITH UNLIKE ATTRIBUTES. THE CALLING PROGRAM PASSES
*THE APPROPRIATE DCB ADDRESS AS A PARAMETER. THIS PROGRAM SETS
*THE DCB MODIFICATION BIT AT DCB+48, AND RETURNS TO THE CALLER.
*THE DCB MUST HAVE BEEN OPENED PRIOR TO CALLING THIS SUBROUTINE.
*
*AUTHOR R. THORNTON  OCT, 1974
*
*
         L     R1,0(R1)                    @ DCB
         OI    48(R1),X'08'                SET DCB MOD. BIT
         BR    R14                         RETURN TO CALLER
R1       EQU   1
R14      EQU   14
         END
